name: Kiki's Colours | Kiki's Playground #5
description: Kiki's Playground is a way for new and experienced artists to come in and find inspiration and have a platform to make a little pocket change at the same time. The deal is the same every time, create what Kiki inspires you to create. The cut is 60%/40% with the artist retaining the majority split. Anyone who's interested will be able to have their submission minted, and I'll take care of the cents for the mint fee. Interested artists can reach out to me on Twitter @BadlyNFT. Artist: @Durnzno
